HEADWORD: Owner
<hw>Own"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who owns; a
rightful proprietor; one who has the legal or rightful title, whether he
is the possessor or not.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
